    body
      header
      main
        .hero.bg-dark.py-5
          .container.text-center.text-light
            h2.mb-3 Find Your Perfect Pair of Shoes
            p.mb-5 Read our expert reviews and find the best shoes for your needs.
            div(class='button-group')
              a.btn.btn-primary(href='login') Log In
              a.btn.btn-primary(href='signup') Sign Up
        .features.py-5
          .container
            .row.text-center
              .col-md-4.mb-4
                i.bi.bi-check2-circle.text-primary.fs-1.mb-3
                h3.mb-3 Expert Reviews
                p Our team of shoe experts test and review the latest shoes on the market.
              .col-md-4.mb-4
                i.bi.bi-star-fill.text-primary.fs-1.mb-3
                h3.mb-3 Top Rated Shoes
                p Discover the shoes that our experts have rated as the best of the best.
              .col-md-4.mb-4
                i.bi.bi-chat-dots-fill.text-primary.fs-1.mb-3
                h3.mb-3 User Reviews
                p Read reviews from other shoe enthusiasts and share your own experiences.
      footer.bg-light.text-center.py-3
        p &copy; 2023 Shoe Review Website
